  # Health Check Endpoint
  
  Used by ECS and load balancers to verify the API is running and responsive.
  
  ## Response
  Returns:
  - `status`: "healthy"
  - `timestamp`: Current UTC timestamp
  - `version`: API version
  
  ## Use Cases
  - Load balancer health checks
  - Monitoring and alerting
  - Service discovery
}
